A. Batch use-case
-----------------

A.1. Files -> Parquet on Alluxio/HDFS [tested]
A.2. Files -> Parquet on Alluxio/S3 [tested]
 
A.3. SQL Access Layer1: HiveQL <-> Parquet on Alluxio/HDFS
A.4. SQL Access Layer1: HiveQL <-> Parquet on Alluxio/S3
 
A.5. SQL Access Layer2: SparkSQL <-> Parquet on Alluxio/HDFS
A.6. SQL Access Layer2: SparkSQL <-> Parquet on Alluxio/S3
 
 
B. Realtime use-case
--------------------
 
B.1. Stream -> HBase -> Alluxio/HDFS
B.2. Stream -> HBase -> Alluxio/S3
 
B.3. To Parquet: HBase (Hive storage handler) -> Parquet on Alluxio/HDFS
B.4. To Parquet: HBase (Hive storage handler) -> Parquet on Alluxio/S3
 
B.5. To Parquet: HBase (SparkSQL) -> Parquet on Alluxio/HDFS
B.6. To Parquet: HBase (SparkSQL) -> Parquet on Alluxio/S3
 
B.7. SQL Access Layer4: HiveQL <-> HBase (Hive storage handler) on Alluxio/HDFS
B.8. SQL Access Layer4: HiveQL <-> HBase (Hive storage handler) on Alluxio/S3
 
B.9. SQL Access Layer5: SparkSQL <-> HBase on Alluxio/HDFS
B.10. SQL Access Layer5: SparkSQL <-> HBase on Alluxio/S3
